title: Update aws-sdk-s3 requirement from 0.25.0 to 0.26.0
body:

title: Fix issue where cache folder would not be created
body: Cache folder would not be created because we used fs::metadata which returns an io::Error with ErrorKind::NotFound if it does not exist. We returned this error, instead of creating the folder.
